fields.Title: WHIRLING F2 / DREAM 5
fields.Description: You are the murderer here dream.

fields.Title: START
input
Ancient Reptilian Brain: "We're trying to help you. All these..."
fields.Dialogue Text: We're trying to help you. All these processes -- these tortures, voices and tremors -- are all just *distractions*. Flares and countermeasures. To keep you from the *last dream*. The worst of them all.

fields.Title: You: "Her face forms in summertime..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Her face forms in summertime...

fields.Title: You: "The... last dream?"
fields.Dialogue Text: The... last dream?

fields.Title: Volition: "They're right. This is their functi..."
fields.Dialogue Text: They're right. This is their function. To keep you from *it*.

fields.Title: Limbic System: "The last dream will be total annihi..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The last dream will be total annihilation. Cinders peeling off the fuselage. We won't be there to help you anymore, Harry. We will be dormant. You will be naked and alone.

fields.Title: Limbic System: "Your eyelids flutter open for a mom..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Your eyelids flutter open for a moment. When you close them again, you sense the light of the room around you -- you're back. In two seconds the alarm will ring.

fields.Title: Untitled hub
You: "Doesn't sound like it will be okay."
fields.Dialogue Text: Doesn't sound like it will be okay.

fields.Title: Variable["church.stained_greeting_done"]
Variable["church.stained_greeting_done"]
!(Variable["church.stained_greeting_done"])
You: "[Open your eyes.]"
fields.Dialogue Text: [Open your eyes.]

fields.Title: Ancient Reptilian Brain: "Of hell and ancient sadness, brothe..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Of hell and ancient sadness, brother. Ten thousand years later -- in front of the video rental. There is a warm breath on your face again. Everything is *okay* again.

fields.Title: Inland Empire: "The last thought in your head befor..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The last thought in your head before waking is: maybe you shouldn't have seen that stained glass window? In the church....

fields.Title: Limbic System: "Hear that? He doesn't even flinch...."
fields.Dialogue Text: Hear that? He doesn't even flinch. Ice-man doesn't care about killing people. That's *nothing* to him. Black water under the bridge. The thing he's *really* scared of...

fields.Title: You: "Great. This is gonna be really chil..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Great. This is gonna be really chill.

fields.Title: You: "Shut up, I just want to sleep."
fields.Dialogue Text: Shut up, I just want to sleep.

fields.Title: You: "And the air will smell of apricots...."
fields.Dialogue Text: And the air will smell of apricots...

fields.Title: You: "I don't care. That doesn't scare me..."
fields.Dialogue Text: I don't care. That doesn't scare me.

fields.Title: Ancient Reptilian Brain: "How've things been going for you ou..."
fields.Dialogue Text: How've things been going for you out there? Helped anyone lately? Saved anyone lately? *Murdered* anyone lately?

fields.Title: Untitled hub (02)
Ancient Reptilian Brain: "Don't tell him, sister. It's too ba..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Don't tell him, sister. It's too bad.

fields.Title: Limbic System: "Like a deftly cast fishing net, sle..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Like a deftly cast fishing net, sleep pulls you out of the world and into its dark shore. The rough mesh chafes, then, tightening around you, it digs into your brain.

fields.Title: Ancient Reptilian Brain: "Because, you know, you *are* a murd..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Because, you know, you *are* a murderer. A disco music listening psycho-killer who offs poor people -- and then *forgets* about it.

fields.Title: Ancient Reptilian Brain: "...in hell and ancient sadness, bro..."
fields.Dialogue Text: ...in hell and ancient sadness, brother. Ten thousand years later -- in front of the video rental. There is a warm breath on your face again. Everything is *okay* again.

fields.Title: Untitled hub
You: "Why are you doing this? I just want..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Why are you doing this? I just want to sleep. I can almost see the dark.

fields.Title: You: "I don't *want to* anymore. I don't..."
fields.Dialogue Text: I don't *want to* anymore. I don't want to think either one of those things.

fields.Title: Limbic System: "...is much, *much* worse than that."
fields.Dialogue Text: ...is much, *much* worse than that.

fields.Title: You: "Yeah-yeah, just let me sleep..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Yeah-yeah, just let me sleep...

fields.Title: Ancient Reptilian Brain: "Oh, but you *will*. You're already..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Oh, but you *will*. You're already *going* there. Slipping. How long can we keep you from the precipice? *One* more dream? Two max, baby. Then it's...

fields.Title: Limbic System: "Everything is *so* okay."
fields.Dialogue Text: Everything is *so* okay.

fields.Title: You: "What is it?"
fields.Dialogue Text: What is it?

fields.Title: You: "Dark shore, my ass. I know what thi..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Dark shore, my ass. I know what this is.

fields.Title: Rhetoric: "This bastard isn't even listening t..."
fields.Dialogue Text: This bastard isn't even listening to you!

fields.Title: Limbic System: "Hear that? You were *naive* to thin..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Hear that? You were *naive* to think he's afraid of his bloodied hands, soul brother. Oh no, I see inside his amygdala and his hippocampus. The thing he's *really* scared of...

fields.Title: You: "Okay, so I'm a murderer and that's..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Okay, so I'm a murderer and that's *bad*.

fields.Title: Limbic System: "Hear that? Ice-man wants to sleep,..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Hear that? Ice-man wants to sleep, he doesn't care about killing people. That's *nothing* to him. Black water under the bridge. The thing he's *really* scared of...

fields.Title: You: "I can't wait. I can't wait..."
fields.Dialogue Text: I can't wait. I can't wait...

fields.Title: Inland Empire: "The last thought in your head befor..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The last thought in your head before waking is: you need to go to the church...
